headline: Generac CEO talks push into data centers
summary: Generac (GNRC) shares soared after posting better-than-expected Q2 results. One of the things that has investors excited is its push into providing generators for data centers. In the video above, the company's chairman, CEO, and president, Aaron Jagdfeld, discusses that opportunity and the impact of tariffs on the business. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Asking for a Trend.
